You can use [innerHTML][1] to insert your button (or toggle a class to show/hide it) and then remove all `flipped` class via a [function][2] &amp; [looping][3] on this class.

example *(probably not the shortest way to do it)*

&lt;!-- begin snippet: js hide: false console: false babel: false --&gt;

